{
  "stem": "13911.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they immediately burned up the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I guess-- no-- no proof, no-- it's-- it's clean.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Erased all the-- not really, but erased the evidence, kind of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and we are just-- and this was happening-- this was not on the 15th day, this-- immediately, in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just sit there in that attic, and we don't know what-- will it ever end?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happens next?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No idea.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But on the 15th days-- 15th day, we look out through the cracks, and we see Germans, and we see a group of people, you know, walking like-- like skeletons, like-- couldn't be any-- anybody else but Jews, you know?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The pogrom ended.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and those remaining-- they weren't going to exterminate all, only 19,000-- Germans, it has to be-- even if would be 19,001, no good. 19,000.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And immediately, we could tell they are Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Are they taking them to work, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you could see, like, watching like-- like-- bent, no life, no-- no soul in them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like they just-- vegetables.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we said, hey, this looks like it's over, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, slowly-- you didn't hear shooting anymore, crying, screaming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no chaos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Quiet.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And slowly, we started-- we-- we could tell for sure it's Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we saw more coming out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we decided that it must be over, after 15 days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "During the 15 days, you mentioned there was one day that you were able to get water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This brave young man--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only time.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only time.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, for your personal needs, you know, we were just doing in front of the others, you know, in a corner.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there were no facilities, you know, to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, you know, lucky, nobody needed to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
